    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Communities, relatively large in size, that are the location of a cathedral, which is the principal church of a Christian diocese and seat of the bishop, archbishop, primate, or patriarch.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
